WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.104
Article 22 is routinely used by Supervisors and Department

00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:07.640
Officials as they address outstanding to unacceptable

00:00:07.707 --> 00:00:10.243
performance by Bargaining Unit Employees.

00:00:10.310 --> 00:00:15.348
Human Resources staff and Union Reps also need to apply various

00:00:15.415 --> 00:00:17.617
provisions of this Article.

00:00:17.684 --> 00:00:21.788
Title 5 and Hybrid Title 38 Bargaining Unit Employees use

00:00:21.855 --> 00:00:23.656
this article when they have questions about their

00:00:23.723 --> 00:00:25.225
performance appraisals.


